---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/ui/PageHero.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';

const values = [
  { title: 'Intelligence over data', desc: "Raw data isn't useful if you don't know what to do with it. Every output from Kaldon is a recommendation, not a spreadsheet. We tell you what to do, not just what the numbers say." },
  { title: 'Connection over collection', desc: "Features that don't connect are just features. We build every capability to feed the next one. Research becomes brand. Brand becomes content. Content becomes revenue." },
  { title: 'Honesty over hype', desc: "We don't promise overnight success. We don't claim AI will replace your judgment. We build tools that make your judgment better and your execution faster. The work is still yours." },
  { title: 'Accessibility over exclusivity', desc: "Professional-grade eCommerce intelligence shouldn't require a $10,000 agency retainer. First-time sellers get the same quality output as 10-year veterans." },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Kaldon — Built by Sellers, for Sellers"
  description="Kaldon was built by eCommerce sellers tired of stitching together 6 tools to launch a product. One connected pipeline. From research to revenue."
>
  <PageHero
    kicker="About"
    headline="Built by sellers who were tired of cloning what's already selling."
    subhead="Kaldon wasn't built in a Silicon Valley office. It was built by people who have launched products, managed inventory, and stayed up at 2am optimizing PPC — and who got tired of research tools that only show you what to clone. We built the platform that finds what the market is actually demanding, and helps you ship it."
  />

  <!-- Origin story -->
  <section class="section-spacing" style="background: var(--void);">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <div class="rounded-card p-8 md:p-10" style="background: var(--deep-space); border: 1px solid var(--hairline);">
        <span class="kicker" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Origin Story</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 28px); line-height: 1.25; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--chalk); margin-bottom: 20px;">
          The tools all show you what's already selling. Nothing points you toward what nobody's built yet.
        </h2>
        <div class="prose-content">
          <p>In 2024, our founder Sean Travis was launching his fourth eCommerce brand. He had the process down: research products in Helium 10, design the brand in Canva, write content in Jasper, schedule posts in Later, build the store in Shopify, manage ads in Meta.</p>
          <p>Six tools. Six logins. Six subscriptions totaling $300+ per month. And the worst part — none of them talked to each other. Every time he found a winning product, he spent 200+ hours manually transferring data between platforms, re-entering the same information, and fighting to maintain brand consistency across disconnected tools.</p>
          <p>The research was excellent. The tools were excellent. But the workflow was broken. The gap wasn't in any individual tool — the gap was between them.</p>
          <p>So he started building. What if product research data automatically became a brand brief? What if the brand identity automatically applied to every piece of content? What if the content automatically populated a store? What if the store data automatically optimized the ads?</p>
          <p>That question became Kaldon — a single platform where every phase of launching and growing an eCommerce product is connected. Not bolted together. Not integrated through Zapier. Connected at the data layer, so intelligence flows from research to revenue without manual intervention.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission -->
  <section class="section-spacing" style="background: var(--void);">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-prose text-center">
      <span class="kicker">Our Mission</span>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--chalk);">
        Turn the market's unmet demand into the next generation of products.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-body-lg" style="color: var(--ghost); line-height: 1.55;">
        The barrier to building a new product shouldn't be how many tools you can afford, how many freelancers you can coordinate, or how well you can guess. Kaldon reads the market for you, validates what to build, finds a supplier who can actually make it, and walks you from concept to live business. The only requirement from you is ambition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="section-spacing" style="background: var(--void);">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <header class="text-center mb-10">
        <span class="kicker">What we believe</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--chalk);">
          Four principles that shape every decision.
        </h2>
      </header>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {values.map((v, i) => (
          <div class="value-card">
            <span class="value-num">{String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            <h3 class="value-title">{v.title}</h3>
            <p class="value-body">{v.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="section-spacing" style="background: var(--void);">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <header class="text-center mb-10">
        <span class="kicker">Founder</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 40px); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--chalk);">
          Sean Travis
        </h2>
      </header>
      <div class="rounded-card p-8 md:p-10" style="background: var(--deep-space); border: 1px solid var(--hairline);">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-5 mb-6 pb-6" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);">
          <div class="founder-avatar" aria-hidden="true">ST</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-semibold" style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; color: var(--chalk); letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Sean Travis</h3>
            <p class="text-body-sm mt-1" style="color: var(--gold);">Founder & CEO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="prose-content">
          <p>Sean has been building eCommerce businesses since 2019. He has launched products on Amazon, Walmart, and DTC, managed six-figure ad budgets, and experienced every pain point that Kaldon now solves.</p>
          <p>Before Kaldon, Sean ran eCommerce operations for multiple brands, learning firsthand that the biggest bottleneck wasn't finding good products — it was everything that came after: building the brand, creating the content, launching the store, scaling the marketing. The tools existed. The workflow was broken.</p>
          <p>Kaldon is the platform Sean wished he had when he launched his first product. It's built with the conviction that eCommerce should be accessible to anyone with a good idea and the willingness to work.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="section-spacing-lg relative overflow-hidden" style="background: var(--void);">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px; -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 0%, transparent 75%); mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, black 0%, transparent 75%);"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10 text-center max-w-prose mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display" style="font-weight: 500; font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 48px); line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.022em; color: var(--chalk);">
        Join the pipeline.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-body-lg" style="color: var(--ghost);">
        2 free analyses. No credit card. See what connected intelligence looks like.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <Button variant="primary" size="large" href="https://kaldon.io/signup" data-event="about_final_cta">
          Start Free — 2 Analyses Included
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5-5 5M6 12h12"/>
          </svg>
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose-content { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
  .prose-content p { font-size: 15.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--ghost); letter-spacing: -0.005em; }

  .value-card { padding: 28px; background: var(--deep-space); border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 12px; transition: border-color 160ms var(--ease-out-quad); }
  .value-card:hover { border-color: var(--hairline-active); }
  .value-num { display: block; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .value-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; color: var(--chalk); letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .value-body { font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ghost); letter-spacing: -0.005em; }

  .founder-avatar {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--void);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline-active);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--chalk);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
</style>
